{"lemma":"كَتَبَة","slug":"كَتَبَة","root":"ك.ت.ب","root_slug":"ك-ت-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ك-ت-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"كاتِب","root":"كتب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":6},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n36626","n36631","n36632"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%83%D9%8E%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to keep up a correspondence, to correspond with"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"active participle of كَتَبَ (kataba): writing","tags":["active","form-of","participle"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"writer; author"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"copyist","examples":[{"text":"وَإِن كُنتُمْ عَلَىٰ سَفَرٍ وَلَمْ تَجِدُوا كَاتِبًا فَرِهَانٌ مَّقْبُوضَةٌ"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"clerk"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"secretary"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"secretary bird, a bird of the species Sagittarius serpentarius."}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of كَتَبَ (kataba, “to write”). Compare Hebrew כותב."},"ipa":["/kaː.ta.ba/","/kaː.tib/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n36626","headword_ar":"كَتَبَهُ","root":"ktb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"katobN","text_ar":"كَتْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitaAbN","text_ar":"كِتَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitaAbapN","text_ar":"كِتَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitobapN","text_ar":"كِتْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) the first of these inf. ns. agreeable with analogy; the second, anomalous; (TA;) or the latter of these two is a subst., like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"libaAsN","text_ar":"لِبَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Lh;) or originally an inf. n., and afterwards used in the senses given"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2590},{"kind":"text","text":"below; (MF;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitaAbapN","text_ar":"كِتَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitobapN","text_ar":"كِتْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kt~bhu","text_ar":"كتّبهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Akttbhu","text_ar":"اكتتبهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He wrote it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"katabahu","text_ar":"كَتَبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has this signification; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Akttbhu","text_ar":"اكتتبهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astktbhu","text_ar":"استكتبهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he asked"},{"kind":"text","text":"[one]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to dictate it"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_isotamolaAhu","text_ar":"اـِسْتَمْلَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (K:) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ikotatabahaA","text_ar":"اـِكْتَتَبَهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the Kur, xxv. 6, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he hath written them"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for himself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he hath asked"},{"kind":"text","text":"[one]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to write them for him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to dictate them"},{"kind":"text","text":"to him. (TA, Bd.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kataba Eanohu","text_ar":"كَتَبَ عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He wrote what he had heard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"learned from him."},{"kind":"text","text":"] A phrase of common occurrence in biographies. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kataba","text_ar":"كَتَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was a writer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scribe, and a learned man."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Implied in the S, where we are referred to the Kur, lii. 41, and lxviii., 47, in illustration of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAtibN","text_ar":"كَاتِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as signifying “ a learned man. ”)]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kataba","text_ar":"كَتَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitaAbN","text_ar":"كِتَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v., (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(God)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prescribed, appointed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ordained,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and made obligatory."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kutiba Ealayokumu AlqiSaASu","text_ar":"كُتِبَ عَلَيْكُمُ القِصَاصُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The law of retaliation is prescribed, appointed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ordained, as a law of which the observance is incumbent on you."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kur, ii. 173.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kutiba Ealayokumu","text_ar":"كُتِبَ عَلَيْكُمُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~iyaAmu","text_ar":"الصِّيَامُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fasting is prescribed as incumbent on you."},{"kind":"text","text":"[Kur. ii. 179.] (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kataba Ealayohi ka*aA","text_ar":"كَتَبَ عَلَيْهِ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He judged, passed sentence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"decreed, against him that he should do such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ktb","text_ar":"كتب"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqaADiY biAln~afaqapi","text_ar":"القَاضِى بِالنَّفَقَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The judge gave sentence that the expenses should be paid."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kataba","text_ar":"كَتَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"katobN","text_ar":"كَتْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drew together; brought together; conjoined."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b2-  Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kataba Albagolapa","text_ar":"كَتَبَ البَغْلَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"katobN","text_ar":"كَتْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He conjoined the oræ of the mule's vulva by means of a ring"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thong;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kataba EalayohaA","text_ar":"كَتَبَ عَلَيْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kataba","text_ar":"كَتَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"katobN","text_ar":"كَتْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kataba EalayohaA","text_ar":"كَتَبَ عَلَيْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He closed the camel's vulva,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and put a ring upon it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he put a ring of iron"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like upon it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conjoining the oræ, in order that she might not be covered."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kataba","text_ar":"كَتَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"katobN","text_ar":"كَتْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Akttb","text_ar":"اكتتب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sewed"},{"kind":"text","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qirobap","text_ar":"قِرْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siqaA='","text_ar":"سِقَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mazaAdap","text_ar":"مَزَادَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with two thongs:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or, accord. to some,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he closed"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at the mouth, by binding it round with a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wikaA'","text_ar":"وِكَاء"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that nothing"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of its contents"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"should drop from it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) [as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aktb","text_ar":"اكتب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":":] or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ktb","text_ar":"كتب"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sewed"},{"kind":"text","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qrbp","text_ar":"قربة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aktb","text_ar":"اكتب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he bound"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wkA='","text_ar":"وكا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bound"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"round the upper part."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kataba","text_ar":"كَتَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"katobN","text_ar":"كَتْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aktb","text_ar":"اكتب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Akttb","text_ar":"اكتتب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bound"},{"kind":"text","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qirobap","text_ar":"قِرْبَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wikaA'","text_ar":"وِكَاء"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he bound"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"round the head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upper part:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or the first of these verbs signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sewed"},{"kind":"text","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qrbp","text_ar":"قربة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Lh.) See above. IAar says, I heard an Arab of the desert say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akotabotu fama","text_ar":"اَكْتَبْتُ فَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~iqaA' falamo yasotakotibo","text_ar":"السِّقَاء فَلَمْ يَسْتَكْتِبْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I bound the mouth of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sqA'","text_ar":"سقاء"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but it did not become fast bound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"closed, because of its hardness and thickness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kataba","text_ar":"كَتَبَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAqapa","text_ar":"النَّاقَةَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He used art to make the she-camel take a liking to that which was not her own young one, and put something as a ring through her nostrils, lest she should smell the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baw~","text_ar":"بَوّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (in some copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bawol","text_ar":"بَوْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but this is a mistake; TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and not have a fondness for it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kataba","text_ar":"كَتَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He collected"},{"kind":"text","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"katiybap","text_ar":"كَتِيبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) See also 2."}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","Bd","God"]},{"entry_id":"n36631","headword_ar":"كُتْبَةٌ","root":"ktb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thong with which one sews"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mazaAdap","text_ar":"مَزَادَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qirobap","text_ar":"قِرْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kutabN","text_ar":"كُتَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That with which the vulva of a camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"(or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a mule,"},{"kind":"text","text":"TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is closed in order that she may not be covered:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kutabN","text_ar":"كُتَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A seam"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suture,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL, PS,) in a skin or hide; (KL;) [app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made by sewing together two edges so that one laps over the other;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurozapN","text_ar":"خُرْزَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whereof the thong conjoins the two faces"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sides"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xrzp","text_ar":"خرزة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is joined together with a thong:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that whereof the thong conjoins each of the two faces"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sides"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (ISd, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kutabN","text_ar":"كُتَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Mgh.)"}],"source_refs":["K","KL","PS","S","Mgh","Lth","ISd","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n36632","headword_ar":"كِتْبَةٌ","root":"ktb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 1 and 8. ―         -b2-  [Also, agreeably with analogy,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, of writing."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}